1
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,340
Yingzi

2
00:01:59,819 --> 00:02:01,040
I have something to tell you

3
00:02:04,180 --> 00:02:04,659
Go ahead

4
00:02:15,860 --> 00:02:17,900
I thought you couldn't drink

5
00:02:18,300 --> 00:02:20,080
Why did you steal a can of booze?

6
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:25,979
You...

7
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,699
what exactly do you want to say?

8
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,180
I...

9
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:37,500
Okay

10
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,580
Then I'm going to say it

11
00:02:44,780 --> 00:02:45,860
Stand still

12
00:02:48,099 --> 00:02:48,879
Don't wobble

13
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:49,860
Listen to me

14
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:51,659
When was I wobbling?

15
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:53,639
You're the one who's unsteady

16
00:02:54,740 --> 00:02:55,300
Okay

17
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:56,840
I...

18
00:02:58,020 --> 00:02:58,379
I...

19
00:02:59,219 --> 00:03:00,240
I want to tell you...

20
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,259
What's wrong, child?

21
00:03:22,020 --> 00:03:23,020
Nothing, Auntie Cai

22
00:03:23,259 --> 00:03:24,599
You don't look well

23
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:26,800
Maybe I drank too much yesterday

24
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,219
Let me feel

25
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,419
It's nothing

26
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:31,620
Honey water

27
00:03:32,259 --> 00:03:34,120
Drinking this helps with a hangover

28
00:03:37,659 --> 00:03:39,740
Look how good Yingzi is to you

29
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,360
Auntie Cai

30
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:53,620
What's the matter?

31
00:03:53,620 --> 00:03:55,060
You're acting so mysterious

32
00:03:57,719 --> 00:03:58,259
Spit it out

33
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:01,759
Will you confess and be treated leniently,

34
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:03,960
or make me say it and be punished severely?

35
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,099
What is it?

36
00:04:05,099 --> 00:04:06,659
What's this about confessing and resisting?

37
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:08,860
You dragged me into the room without a word

38
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,759
I don't even know what you want to ask

39
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,719
You think I didn't see it?

40
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,420
Give up the fantasy, little girl

41
00:04:19,259 --> 00:04:20,959
Professionals like us...

42
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:22,939
can smell it a mile away

43
00:04:23,420 --> 00:04:25,579
What is it exactly?

44
00:04:26,579 --> 00:04:27,180
You...

45
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:28,740
and that Yusheng...

46
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:30,480
have something going on

47
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,220
Wha...

48
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,040
What's going on?

49
00:04:35,459 --> 00:04:36,860
The way he looks at you isn't right

50
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,540
No...

51
00:04:39,339 --> 00:04:40,120
There isn't

52
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:42,699
The way you look at him isn't right either

53
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,740
No

54
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:46,680
Auntie Cai, you're allergic

55
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,000
You're being overly sensitive

56
00:04:48,199 --> 00:04:49,600
Me, allergic?

57
00:04:49,779 --> 00:04:51,240
Who am I?

58
00:04:52,459 --> 00:04:53,759
Matchmaking...

59
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:56,160
has given me a pair of eagle eyes

60
00:04:56,379 --> 00:04:58,680
If two mosquitoes fly past me,

61
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,480
I can tell the male from the female instantly

62
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:02,379
If two people pass by me,

63
00:05:02,379 --> 00:05:03,279
I can immediately see...

64
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:04,480
if there's any hanky-panky,

65
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:06,339
or if it's true love

66
00:05:08,019 --> 00:05:08,839
Little girl...

67
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:10,519
Tell me the truth

68
00:05:11,779 --> 00:05:12,839
Do you have feelings...

69
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,420
for Yusheng?

70
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:24,120
You silly child.

71
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:25,980
Why?

72
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:28,160
You mean I shouldn't like him?

73
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:28,920
No.

74
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,379
You should like him.

75
00:05:30,579 --> 00:05:31,740
I said you're silly...

76
00:05:31,899 --> 00:05:33,339
because you kept it from me.

77
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:34,839
Who am I?

78
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:37,879
I'm Cupid.

79
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:38,420
Right?

80
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,660
You should have told me first thing.

81
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,240
Right?

82
00:05:42,220 --> 00:05:42,920
Alright.

83
00:05:43,139 --> 00:05:45,860
Since I know you have feelings for Yusheng...

84
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:48,019
then this is out of your hands.

85
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:50,019
Out of my hands?

86
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:50,779
That's right.

87
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,339
Just leave it to Auntie Cai.

88
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:54,220
Any problem, I'll solve it in a jiffy.

89
00:05:54,379 --> 00:05:54,819
You...

90
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,540
You...

91
00:05:57,019 --> 00:05:58,379
How do you plan to solve it?

92
00:05:59,139 --> 00:05:59,680
Yusheng!

93
00:06:01,259 --> 00:06:01,759
Auntie Cai.

94
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:02,540
Stop sweeping. Come here.

95
00:06:02,579 --> 00:06:03,220
I have something to tell you.

96
00:06:04,339 --> 00:06:05,800
What is it, Auntie Cai?

97
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,600
You look so serious.

98
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,439
Be serious.

99
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:09,899
It's a big deal.

100
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:13,220
To call it a turning point in your life...

101
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,079
is not an exaggeration at all.

102
00:06:15,060 --> 00:06:16,160
It concerns...

103
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,740
your life's happiness.

104
00:06:19,819 --> 00:06:21,519
It might mean that...

105
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,199
from now on...

106
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:25,360
you won't just have one dad...

107
00:06:25,459 --> 00:06:26,560
and one mom.

108
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:29,339
What does that mean?

109
00:06:29,759 --> 00:06:31,100
Parents are the kind of relatives...

110
00:06:31,139 --> 00:06:32,160
the more the merrier?

111
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:33,180
Keep a few backups?

112
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:34,160
What do I need backups for?

113
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,279
What is this child talking about?

114
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:38,560
Yusheng.

115
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,759
I'm asking you.

116
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,579
Are you willing?

117
00:06:41,579 --> 00:06:42,319
Auntie Cai! I'm willing!

118
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,079
What are you doing?

119
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:46,860
No...

120
00:06:47,019 --> 00:06:48,300
Are you crazy, child?

121
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:49,000
I...

122
00:06:49,139 --> 00:06:50,819
was just getting to the crucial part.

123
00:06:50,899 --> 00:06:51,500
No...

124
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,699
I think this matter...

125
00:06:53,779 --> 00:06:55,800
is a major life decision for me.

126
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,399
It can't be spoken by someone else.

127
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:59,079
I must say it myself.

128
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:01,160
Otherwise, I'll regret it for the rest of my life.

129
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:03,660
That makes sense.

130
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,660
This girl is something.

131
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,519
A bit like me when I was young.

132
00:07:08,100 --> 00:07:08,800
How about this.

133
00:07:09,379 --> 00:07:10,639
I'll keep watch here for you.

134
00:07:11,439 --> 00:07:12,360
You tell him yourself.

135
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,139
No.

136
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:16,620
No need to keep watch.

137
00:07:16,860 --> 00:07:18,540
I'll tell him myself.

138
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:19,860
You go back to your room and rest.

139
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:20,660
What?

140
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,240
How can I rest at a time like this?

141
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,100
You're so funny.

142
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:23,759
How about this.

143
00:07:24,699 --> 00:07:25,279
You go ahead.

144
00:07:25,579 --> 00:07:26,100
And I...

145
00:07:26,100 --> 00:07:27,519
will watch from here. No.

146
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,459
With you staring at me here...

147
00:07:32,459 --> 00:07:33,639
I can't say it.

148
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:34,759
Go back to your room, Auntie Cai.

149
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,279
This...

150
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,480
Can you say it yourself then?

151
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:37,060
I can say it.

152
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,540
I can.

153
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:38,339
Say it properly.

154
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:39,000
Say it properly.

155
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,540
What were you two chatting about just now?

156
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:51,399
Whispering like that.

157
00:07:51,699 --> 00:07:52,420
Well...

158
00:07:53,139 --> 00:07:55,160
What Auntie Cai said just now...

159
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:56,579
Did you understand it?

160
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,019
No.

161
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,040
What did Auntie Cai mean?

162
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,899
How could you...

163
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:02,879
really not understand a thing?

164
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,540
I really didn't.

165
00:08:05,699 --> 00:08:07,000
Do you know what she meant?

166
00:08:07,459 --> 00:08:08,819
I don't either...

167
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,120
But my guess is...

168
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:12,540
maybe...

169
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:14,279
Auntie Cai wanted to ask you...

170
00:08:14,899 --> 00:08:16,120
if you'd be willing...

171
00:08:16,300 --> 00:08:17,180
to take her as your godmother.

172
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,620
What is this?

173
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:21,199
What kind of situation is this?

174
00:08:21,459 --> 00:08:23,000
I failed at the big match,

175
00:08:23,420 --> 00:08:25,279
and you find me a godson instead?

176
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,480
Don't you think that's good?

177
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:30,199
Don't you usually like Yusheng the most?

178
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,019
Yes.

179
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,679
The kid is nice enough.

180
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:34,399
But that still won't do!

181
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,740
I failed at this match.

182
00:08:36,779 --> 00:08:37,580
In my...

183
00:08:37,740 --> 00:08:39,019
matchmaking...

184
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,279
career of benefiting mankind,

185
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,720
I've got a black mark.

186
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,279
It's a real blemish.

187
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,840
For my career...

188
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,519
let me tell you,

189
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:48,559
it's my biggest stain now.

190
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,700
If word gets out,

191
00:08:50,419 --> 00:08:53,000
what will the industry elites think of me?

192
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,559
My lifetime reputation...

193
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:57,279
ruined in an instant!

194
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,779
Who'd know if I don't tell?

195
00:09:00,299 --> 00:09:01,220
And I beg you,

196
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:02,919
please don't tell anyone else.

197
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:05,980
Who is Auntie Cai?

198
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,679
I have lips of steel.

199
00:09:07,779 --> 00:09:09,200
I'm tight-lipped.

200
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,519
Even severe torture

201
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:13,539
couldn't make me talk.

202
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:20,639
Yingzi, there you are.

203
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:21,299
Hello, Grandma Liu.

204
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:22,919
By the way,

205
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,379
I was just about to tell you.

206
00:09:26,419 --> 00:09:27,879
That kid Yusheng is quite nice.

207
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,419
You have good taste.

208
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:33,340
What choice? What taste?

209
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,419
Don't you like Yusheng?

210
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:37,139
How do you know that?

211
00:09:37,379 --> 00:09:37,700
I...

212
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:38,639
I heard from... uh...

213
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,240
Auntie Luo told me.

214
00:09:40,299 --> 00:09:41,320
Auntie Luo?

215
00:09:42,379 --> 00:09:43,879
How does she know?

216
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,580
Auntie Luo heard it from Grandma Jin.

217
00:09:46,620 --> 00:09:47,600
Grandma Jin?

218
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:48,460
No...

219
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:50,039
How does she know?

220
00:09:50,139 --> 00:09:51,080
Grandma Jin said...

221
00:09:51,139 --> 00:09:52,600
she heard it from Grandpa Gou'er.

222
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,299
Gou'er...

223
00:09:54,299 --> 00:09:55,799
Even Grandpa Gou'er knows?

224
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,659
Then who told Grandpa Gou'er?

225
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,960
Grandpa Gou'er was told by Xiaofang.

226
00:10:00,059 --> 00:10:02,559
Xiaofang was told by Rudy.

227
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,559
And Rudy was...

228
00:10:04,659 --> 00:10:05,820
told by Old Liang.

229
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:06,860
And then Old Liang was...

230
00:10:06,860 --> 00:10:08,279
Oh my god.

231
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:10,100
Doesn't this mean

232
00:10:10,100 --> 00:10:12,279
the whole retirement community knows?

233
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:13,539
Oh my god.

234
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,379
How can I face anyone?

235
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,799
That's on me.

236
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:20,200
My fault.

237
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:20,620
It's all...

238
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,679
uh...

239
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:24,059
Just a moment of carelessness that day.

240
00:10:24,139 --> 00:10:26,399
I just leaked a tiny bit to Old Liang.

241
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:27,600
Auntie Cai,

242
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:30,440
didn't you promise to keep your lips sealed?

243
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,220
That you wouldn't tell even under torture?

244
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:33,960
Well, Old Liang also

245
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:35,519
promised me the same thing.

246
00:10:35,539 --> 00:10:37,919
He said even under torture

247
00:10:37,919 --> 00:10:39,740
he would never tell anyone.

248
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:41,080
That's why I

249
00:10:41,159 --> 00:10:42,759
leaked just a tiny bit to him.

250
00:10:44,379 --> 00:10:45,200
Yingzi,

251
00:10:45,519 --> 00:10:46,580
all secrets,

252
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,340
once Auntie Cai knows them,

253
00:10:48,460 --> 00:10:51,200
the whole retirement community pretty much knows.

254
00:10:51,940 --> 00:10:53,820
Oh my god.

255
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:55,600
Alright.

256
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,379
It's okay.

257
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:58,740
It's not like it's shameful, is it?

258
00:10:59,100 --> 00:10:59,840
Don't worry.

259
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,500
The students don't know.

260
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:03,960
Teacher Liu,

261
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:06,019
hurry and think of a way for the kid.

262
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:07,519
Things are already like this.

263
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:09,019
What's the next step?

264
00:11:09,419 --> 00:11:11,600
As for the next step...

265
00:11:12,940 --> 00:11:13,840
I think...

266
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,759
let's stage a chance encounter.

267
00:11:26,379 --> 00:11:27,000
Auntie Cai

268
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:28,080
Keke

269
00:11:28,139 --> 00:11:28,799
Morning exercise?

270
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:30,840
Can I ask you something?

271
00:11:31,059 --> 00:11:32,820
What is it? Ask away.

272
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:33,919
Auntie Cai,

273
00:11:34,379 --> 00:11:36,320
does Yingzi like Yusheng?

274
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,279
How come you also...

275
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:40,019
know to come ask me?

276
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,940
Who are you?

277
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:44,340
You're the know-it-all of Willow New Town.

278
00:11:44,399 --> 00:11:46,240
Nothing gets past you.

279
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,419
That's for sure.

280
00:11:47,659 --> 00:11:48,480
Not necessarily.

281
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:50,000
I don't know about this.

282
00:11:50,059 --> 00:11:50,620
I'm not clear on it.

283
00:11:51,759 --> 00:11:52,919
Look at you.

284
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:53,960
Why are you...

285
00:11:54,059 --> 00:11:55,700
holding out on me?

286
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,659
Holding out?

287
00:11:57,340 --> 00:11:59,220
I'm not holding out.

288
00:12:00,139 --> 00:12:02,720
I promised Yingzi.

289
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:05,340
Even under torture,

290
00:12:05,399 --> 00:12:06,879
I can't tell anyone else.

291
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:08,799
Then I promise you too.

292
00:12:08,860 --> 00:12:09,840
Even under torture,

293
00:12:09,919 --> 00:12:10,940
I won't tell anyone either.

294
00:12:11,019 --> 00:12:12,500
Never mind torture,

295
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:14,200
even if I'm torn to pieces,

296
00:12:14,259 --> 00:12:15,039
I absolutely won't tell.

297
00:12:15,159 --> 00:12:15,659
That's good.

298
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,759
But it won't work.

299
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:19,700
I already promised Yingzi.

300
00:12:19,980 --> 00:12:22,539
I said I wouldn't tell, so I won't.

301
00:12:22,539 --> 00:12:24,100
Beat me to death and I won't say.

302
00:12:25,399 --> 00:12:26,019
Fine then.

303
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,200
I won't ask.

304
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,360
I've figured it out.

305
00:12:29,799 --> 00:12:31,240
It's not that you won't tell me.

306
00:12:31,379 --> 00:12:33,220
It's that you don't know at all.

307
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:35,580
Don't go!

308
00:12:37,539 --> 00:12:39,159
A warrior can be killed but not humiliated!

309
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,940
There is nothing in Willow New Town...

310
00:12:40,940 --> 00:12:42,980
that your Auntie Cai doesn't know.

311
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:45,139
That's not for sure.

312
00:12:45,259 --> 00:12:47,340
Auntie Cai, even if you know, don't say it.

313
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,659
I don't want to hear it.

314
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,679
Playing hard to get now?

315
00:12:50,419 --> 00:12:51,860
I simply must tell you today.

316
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:53,299
About Yingzi...

317
00:12:56,019 --> 00:12:57,740
Why did I have to promise Yingzi...

318
00:12:57,740 --> 00:12:59,340
to keep her secret?

319
00:12:59,899 --> 00:13:02,720
Holding this in is killing me.

320
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:04,059
Auntie Cai.

321
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:05,580
How about this?

322
00:13:05,679 --> 00:13:06,379
You...

323
00:13:06,580 --> 00:13:07,299
don't say it.

324
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:09,600
Just nod or shake your head.

325
00:13:11,159 --> 00:13:13,659
Does Yingzi like Yusheng?

326
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:17,960
I knew it!

327
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:19,960
There's more you don't know.

328
00:13:21,019 --> 00:13:22,360
Since you guessed this part yourself,

329
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,399
and it wasn't me who told you,

330
00:13:23,399 --> 00:13:24,480
I might as well just...

331
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,759
tell you everything and be done with it.

332
00:13:43,299 --> 00:13:44,679
What happened? You're so careless.

333
00:13:44,919 --> 00:13:45,600
Watch where you're going.

334
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:46,840
It's my fault.

335
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,039
I was walking too fast.

336
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,159
Alright.

337
00:13:49,419 --> 00:13:50,360
Don't worry about it.

338
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:51,559
I'll pick them up myself.

339
00:13:51,899 --> 00:13:52,399
It's fine.

340
00:13:52,399 --> 00:13:53,120
Let me help you carry them.

341
00:13:54,019 --> 00:13:54,460
Here.

342
00:13:56,539 --> 00:13:57,600
Don't worry about it.

343
00:13:57,960 --> 00:14:00,000
Yingzi might get unhappy later.

344
00:14:00,519 --> 00:14:01,240
Yingzi?

345
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,179
Why would she be unhappy?

346
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:04,799
You two...

347
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:07,179
Aren't you together?

348
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:08,240
No.

349
00:14:08,919 --> 00:14:10,019
Not at all.

350
00:14:10,220 --> 00:14:11,620
That's what everyone says.

351
00:14:11,799 --> 00:14:14,080
They say you two have a special relationship.

352
00:14:15,379 --> 00:14:16,159
About the same.

353
00:14:16,740 --> 00:14:18,779
Actually, everyone's relationship is about the same.

354
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:20,559
Maybe because of our work...

355
00:14:20,919 --> 00:14:21,899
...we interact a bit more.

356
00:14:22,700 --> 00:14:25,019
If you're boyfriend and girlfriend, just admit it.

357
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:27,559
What's there to be shy about?

358
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:30,919
But we really aren't.

359
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,340
We're just buddies.

360
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:33,840
Right.

361
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:34,980
Right.

362
00:14:35,460 --> 00:14:36,379
Just buddies.

363
00:14:36,700 --> 00:14:37,960
I thought so.

364
00:14:38,059 --> 00:14:39,639
I'm such good friends with Yingzi.

365
00:14:39,639 --> 00:14:41,700
She never mentioned anything about you two to me.

366
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:44,299
So it seems she really treats you as a buddy.

367
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,320
Let me tell you.

368
00:14:45,399 --> 00:14:47,179
Don't get any bad ideas about my bestie.

369
00:14:47,259 --> 00:14:49,299
Otherwise, if she treats you as a buddy...

370
00:14:49,299 --> 00:14:50,720
...and you don't treat her as a buddy...

371
00:14:51,580 --> 00:14:52,720
...then you are...

372
00:14:53,259 --> 00:14:54,720
...not being a good buddy.

373
00:14:56,620 --> 00:14:57,799
What's wrong?

374
00:14:58,259 --> 00:14:59,799
Did the accidental meeting not work?

375
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,299
It shouldn't have failed.

376
00:15:02,620 --> 00:15:04,720
This trick works every time.

377
00:15:04,899 --> 00:15:06,840
The guy usually follows along obediently.

378
00:15:07,299 --> 00:15:08,700
What's up with this Yusheng?

379
00:15:08,980 --> 00:15:10,679
Didn't he help you pick up the books?

380
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,320
Didn't he help you up?

381
00:15:12,519 --> 00:15:13,220
No.

382
00:15:13,299 --> 00:15:14,700
Rub your knees for you?

383
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:16,120
And then carry you back to the dorm?

384
00:15:16,460 --> 00:15:17,379
No.

385
00:15:18,179 --> 00:15:19,460
Yusheng said...

386
00:15:20,019 --> 00:15:22,259
...he just sees me as a buddy.

387
00:15:23,159 --> 00:15:23,879
This...

388
00:15:24,059 --> 00:15:25,019
What kind of talk is that?

389
00:15:25,019 --> 00:15:26,820
How can he treat you as a buddy, this kid?

390
00:15:27,159 --> 00:15:27,639
Right.

391
00:15:28,059 --> 00:15:29,559
Being buddies isn't bad either.

392
00:15:29,759 --> 00:15:31,500
Being buddies is actually pretty good.

393
00:15:32,059 --> 00:15:33,519
At first, you're buddies.

394
00:15:33,519 --> 00:15:34,519
Then later...

395
00:15:34,559 --> 00:15:36,100
...you become little frenemies.

396
00:15:36,159 --> 00:15:37,720
And then later you start dating.

397
00:15:37,740 --> 00:15:38,259
And then...

398
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,899
So many childhood sweethearts...

399
00:15:39,899 --> 00:15:42,559
...end up as a family, a couple.

400
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:43,639
Little Cai.

401
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,419
Your matchmaking...

402
00:15:45,519 --> 00:15:46,899
...needs to keep up with the times.

403
00:15:47,279 --> 00:15:49,139
Nowadays when young people say...

404
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,779
...buddy or bestie...

405
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:51,899
...what they mean is...

406
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,259
...no feelings.

407
00:15:56,220 --> 00:15:57,539
Is it hopeless?

408
00:15:58,460 --> 00:15:58,840
Well...

409
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,460
What?

410
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:00,019
Let's...

411
00:16:00,019 --> 00:16:01,480
Let's analyze this again.

412
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:02,440
So...

413
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,399
Yingzi.

414
00:16:03,899 --> 00:16:04,379
You...

415
00:16:04,419 --> 00:16:05,340
Listen to me.

416
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:07,019
About Yusheng...

417
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:08,919
What exactly did he say to you?

418
00:16:09,159 --> 00:16:11,120
He didn't tell me directly.

419
00:16:11,519 --> 00:16:12,919
He told Keke.

420
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:13,899
Keke?

421
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,980
Why is Keke in the mix?

422
00:16:16,259 --> 00:16:18,659
I was ready to bump into him.

423
00:16:19,259 --> 00:16:21,519
But before I could do that,

424
00:16:21,919 --> 00:16:24,019
Keke happened to pass by.

425
00:16:24,340 --> 00:16:27,059
So she bumped into him first.

426
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:28,899
Then Yusheng...

427
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,399
helped her up...

428
00:16:30,500 --> 00:16:31,879
and picked up her books.

429
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:34,039
Then Keke asked Yusheng

430
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:36,720
if he was official with Yingzi.

431
00:16:37,059 --> 00:16:38,799
I didn't tell her to say that!

432
00:16:38,799 --> 00:16:39,360
I...

433
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,460
I didn't say anything.

434
00:16:41,259 --> 00:16:42,279
Yusheng said,

435
00:16:42,519 --> 00:16:44,019
"There's nothing between us."

436
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:45,820
Keke asked him again,

437
00:16:46,259 --> 00:16:48,039
"So, just buddies?"

438
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:51,179
Yusheng said, "Just buddies."

439
00:16:52,899 --> 00:16:54,659
Keke is something else.

440
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:55,899
She's playing a slick game.

441
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:57,519
She even spun me around.

442
00:16:57,759 --> 00:16:59,559
Did you say something to Keke?

443
00:16:59,559 --> 00:17:00,379
No.

444
00:17:00,379 --> 00:17:01,460
Absolutely not.

445
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:02,519
Really?

446
00:17:06,019 --> 00:17:06,740
Auntie Cai

447
00:17:06,799 --> 00:17:07,500
Don't call me Auntie Cai.

448
00:17:07,579 --> 00:17:08,539
I'm not your Auntie Cai.

449
00:17:09,079 --> 00:17:10,099
I'm a sucker.

450
00:17:10,980 --> 00:17:12,079
I'm the one being fooled.

451
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:14,180
I'm the one who got sold out,

452
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:15,759
and still counts the money for them.

453
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:17,019
Auntie Cai.

454
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:19,000
Don't praise yourself like that.

455
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:19,900
Nonsense.

456
00:17:20,359 --> 00:17:21,500
Am I praising myself?

457
00:17:21,579 --> 00:17:23,019
How is it not praise?

458
00:17:23,099 --> 00:17:24,579
Didn't you always warn us,

459
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:26,440
that suffering a loss is a blessing?

460
00:17:26,519 --> 00:17:28,039
Always think of others first.

461
00:17:28,039 --> 00:17:29,240
Rather suffer a loss yourself,

462
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,740
than let others be sad.

463
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:32,420
No matter how wronged we feel,

464
00:17:32,420 --> 00:17:33,519
or how unjustly we're treated,

465
00:17:33,599 --> 00:17:34,839
we do it without complaint or regret.

466
00:17:34,839 --> 00:17:36,700
To be a good mediator and leader,

467
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:37,680
a sucker, right?

468
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:40,180
This kid sure knows how to summarize.

469
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,599
To be honest,

470
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:43,759
I really am that kind of person.

471
00:17:43,759 --> 00:17:44,359
Cut it out.

472
00:17:44,359 --> 00:17:45,759
You almost confused me there.

473
00:17:46,279 --> 00:17:47,019
What is this?

474
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,660
What did I come here for?

475
00:17:48,740 --> 00:17:49,779
Did I ask you to praise me?

476
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:51,640
I came to demand an explanation.

477
00:17:52,559 --> 00:17:53,039
I...

478
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:55,039
What crime have I committed?

479
00:17:55,039 --> 00:17:55,700
Let me ask you.

480
00:17:56,519 --> 00:17:57,859
Yusheng and Yingzi...

481
00:17:58,099 --> 00:17:59,259
are buddies.

482
00:17:59,299 --> 00:18:00,160
What's going on?

483
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:02,859
You fished for information from me,

484
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:03,799
then went and ruined things.

485
00:18:03,819 --> 00:18:05,420
You're playing quite a game.

486
00:18:05,759 --> 00:18:06,859
Auntie Cai.

487
00:18:07,019 --> 00:18:07,940
You... Don't pull me.

488
00:18:08,259 --> 00:18:09,720
Why don't you understand?

489
00:18:09,799 --> 00:18:10,160
I...

490
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:12,119
I'm helping Yingzi here.

491
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:12,660
Helping?

492
00:18:13,019 --> 00:18:13,859
I don't see it.

493
00:18:14,740 --> 00:18:16,299
Yingzi has always liked Yusheng.

494
00:18:16,339 --> 00:18:18,259
But she's never dared to confess to him.

495
00:18:18,359 --> 00:18:19,480
What is she afraid of?

496
00:18:20,759 --> 00:18:21,640
What is she afraid of?

497
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,240
Isn't she just afraid...

498
00:18:23,339 --> 00:18:24,799
that she doesn't know where she stands

499
00:18:24,799 --> 00:18:26,119
in Yusheng's heart?

500
00:18:26,259 --> 00:18:27,400
Their relationship...

501
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:29,720
What does Yusheng actually think?

502
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,519
Exactly.

503
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:34,380
So what does Yusheng think in the end?

504
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,559
That's why.

505
00:18:35,619 --> 00:18:37,240
I went to fish for information.

506
00:18:37,299 --> 00:18:38,519
I was helping Yingzi ask,

507
00:18:38,519 --> 00:18:40,140
what Yusheng really thinks of her.

508
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:42,140
Oh, really?

509
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,559
Why didn't you say so earlier?

510
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,160
You were helping them.

511
00:18:48,559 --> 00:18:50,420
Then Auntie Cai blamed you wrongly.

512
00:18:50,559 --> 00:18:51,380
Then...

513
00:18:51,420 --> 00:18:52,299
Then I must apologize to you.

514
00:18:52,299 --> 00:18:53,259
I'm sorry.

515
00:18:53,319 --> 00:18:53,920
It's okay.

516
00:18:54,079 --> 00:18:54,700
No need.

517
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:55,420
Auntie Cai.

518
00:18:55,460 --> 00:18:56,420
Let me tell you,

519
00:18:56,519 --> 00:18:57,799
you are my role model.

520
00:18:57,859 --> 00:18:58,700
My idol.

521
00:18:58,759 --> 00:19:00,200
No matter how wronged we feel,

522
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,500
or how unjustly we're treated,

523
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:03,700
we must be the sucker.

524
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:04,500
Right.

525
00:19:04,599 --> 00:19:05,500
This sucker role,

526
00:19:05,559 --> 00:19:06,819
we're definitely taking it.

527
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,119
Yusheng

528
00:19:15,599 --> 00:19:16,680
There's something

529
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:19,599
I haven't known how to tell you

530
00:19:20,519 --> 00:19:21,859
If you don't know how to tell me

531
00:19:21,859 --> 00:19:22,920
then just don't say it

532
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:25,640
So you mean

533
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,920
you already know what I'm going to say?

534
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:28,740
No, I don't

535
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,839
How would I know what you're going to say?

536
00:19:31,220 --> 00:19:31,779
Then

537
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:34,539
do you want to take a guess?

538
00:19:36,339 --> 00:19:37,059
I'd rather not

539
00:19:37,339 --> 00:19:39,039
I'm not really the guessing type

540
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:40,240
Then I'll just say it straight

541
00:19:41,839 --> 00:19:43,599
What I mean is

542
00:19:43,839 --> 00:19:44,940
actually, I...

543
00:19:45,359 --> 00:19:47,220
have liked you for a long time

544
00:19:47,299 --> 00:19:48,079
Keke

545
00:19:49,839 --> 00:19:51,519
You finally said it

546
00:19:53,319 --> 00:19:54,779
You're really something

547
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:57,440
You kept saying you wanted to help Yingzi

548
00:19:58,259 --> 00:19:59,759
Is this how you help?

549
00:19:59,940 --> 00:20:01,880
This is called poaching

550
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:02,519
Auntie Cai, I...

551
00:20:02,519 --> 00:20:03,400
Don't call me Auntie Cai

552
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,420
I'm just a sucker

553
00:20:04,420 --> 00:20:04,839
Godmother

554
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:05,920
Don't call me Godmother

555
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:09,180
I used to think you were such a good kid

556
00:20:09,619 --> 00:20:12,779
Who knew looks could be so deceiving?

557
00:20:13,140 --> 00:20:15,900
Turns out a scumbag can be handsome too, huh?

558
00:20:16,259 --> 00:20:16,900
Speak up

559
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:19,500
So, what's your toxic trait?

560
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:22,119
I still haven't figured out

561
00:20:22,119 --> 00:20:23,299
who you're talking to

562
00:20:23,319 --> 00:20:24,599
I'm talking to you!

563
00:20:24,799 --> 00:20:26,119
Two-timing!

564
00:20:26,539 --> 00:20:27,500
I...

565
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:28,359
I...

566
00:20:28,839 --> 00:20:31,019
I haven't even got one girl yet

567
00:20:31,660 --> 00:20:32,599
Well, what you said

568
00:20:32,819 --> 00:20:33,519
seems to be true

569
00:20:33,740 --> 00:20:35,279
And I was the one who confessed first

570
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,500
So at the very least

571
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:37,759
it's fair competition, right?

572
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,279
You are simply...

573
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,779
That actually makes sense

574
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:43,119
Besides, I haven't agreed to anything

575
00:20:43,119 --> 00:20:44,579
How am I a scumbag?

576
00:20:45,319 --> 00:20:46,099
You...

577
00:20:46,660 --> 00:20:47,799
I can't out-talk you two

578
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:49,220
Let's cut the chit-chat

579
00:20:49,619 --> 00:20:51,059
Give me a straight answer

580
00:20:51,319 --> 00:20:53,039
Do you like Keke

581
00:20:53,039 --> 00:20:54,359
or do you like Yingzi?

582
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:55,099
I...

583
00:20:57,500 --> 00:20:59,259
How am I supposed to answer that?

584
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:00,539
Speak from your heart

585
00:21:00,819 --> 00:21:02,680
Who do you actually like?

586
00:21:10,420 --> 00:21:11,500
I'm sorry, Keke

587
00:21:12,599 --> 00:21:13,579
I like Yingzi

588
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:17,079
Actually, I've wanted to confess to her for a long time

589
00:21:18,140 --> 00:21:19,299
But her father has been planning

590
00:21:19,299 --> 00:21:20,519
to send her abroad to study

591
00:21:20,819 --> 00:21:22,460
If I really got together with her

592
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:24,259
I would definitely affect her going abroad

593
00:21:24,259 --> 00:21:25,319
and affect her future

594
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:27,700
That would be too selfish of me

595
00:21:27,740 --> 00:21:28,680
Yingzi

596
00:21:28,859 --> 00:21:30,119
did you hear that?

597
00:21:30,799 --> 00:21:31,500
Yingzi?

598
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:32,660
Where is she?

599
00:21:42,740 --> 00:21:43,319
Yingzi!

600
00:21:44,299 --> 00:21:44,960
I'm sorry

601
00:21:46,279 --> 00:21:46,839
Wait, tell me

602
00:21:46,839 --> 00:21:48,680
how come all the good things happen to you?

603
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:50,339
How are you so lucky?

604
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:52,779
Auntie Cai

605
00:21:53,059 --> 00:21:55,220
I'm a girl too, you know

606
00:21:55,359 --> 00:21:57,900
Why do you help her and not me?

607
00:21:58,859 --> 00:22:00,140
Auntie will introduce you to a good one later

608
00:22:00,140 --> 00:22:02,079
Child, don't cry, child
